JUDGMENT:
     CRIMINAL APPELLATE	 JURISDICTION : Criminal Appeal Nos.
461-466 of 1980.
     From  the	 Judgment  &  order  dated  9.11.78  of	 the
Allahabad High	Court in  Criminal  Misc.  Application	Nos.
1655, 1656, 1657, 1691 and 1698 of 1979.
